event,"Hello. This is a journal containing my entry for the <lj comm=""narnia_100""> Icon Challenge.
Please feel free to contact me or comment if you'd like any of the icons. As always, credit me, <lj user=""empressnerd"">, for their usage.

Credits for my icons will be placed in my user profile in a list format. I am sorry I don't have time to credit each individual aspect, but I will try my best. If I have incorrectly credited, or forgotten to credit your works, please feel free to leave a message and I will fix things straight away.
Feel free to add any entries to memories because I update every so often and don't have any more deadlines until all 100 are to be turned in.
